WEBVTT

1
00:00:13.054 --> 00:00:15.432
I want for Geon-woo to be fully recovered.

2
00:00:15.515 --> 00:00:17.851
[uneasy music plays]

3
00:00:17.934 --> 00:00:19.144
That is my wish.

4
00:00:19.644 --> 00:00:22.564
[nurse] Doctor! Patient Kim Geon-woo
is showing spontaneous breathing.

5
00:00:22.647 --> 00:00:24.816
I think you should come see him right now.

6
00:00:24.899 --> 00:00:26.735
[Geon-woo breathes heavily]

7
00:00:27.235 --> 00:00:28.069
WISH GRANTED

8
00:00:28.153 --> 00:00:29.779
[timer ticks]

9
00:00:30.363 --> 00:00:31.197
[Ha-joon sighs]

10
00:00:39.122 --> 00:00:42.125
Ha-joon. come here right away. I can
help you. but it has to be in person.

11
00:00:42.208 --> 00:00:43.168
[music stops]

12
00:00:45.378 --> 00:00:46.421
I have an idea. Se-ah.

13
00:00:46.504 --> 00:00:47.714
[mysterious music plays]

14
00:00:47.797 --> 00:00:49.841
There's someone I think you should meet.

15
00:00:54.804 --> 00:00:55.805
My older sister.

16
00:00:56.389 --> 00:00:57.390
Your sister?

17
00:00:58.475 --> 00:00:59.350
Ha-young?

18
00:01:00.018 --> 00:01:00.852
[Ha-joon] Mm.

19
00:01:01.478 --> 00:01:02.896
You said she was studying abroad.

20
00:01:05.065 --> 00:01:06.066
All that was a lie.

21
00:01:07.108 --> 00:01:09.319
The truth is that I was embarrassed.

22
00:01:10.111 --> 00:01:13.823
She quit her job years ago.
changed her name. and became a shaman.

23
00:01:14.324 --> 00:01:16.409
-[Se-ah] A shaman?
-I didn't want anyone to know.

24
00:01:40.683 --> 00:01:41.935
[driver] Holy shit.

25
00:01:42.519 --> 00:01:46.439
-Is this really the right way?
-Yes. Just keep on following the GPS.

26
00:01:46.523 --> 00:01:49.192
-Please. sir. It's important.
-[driver] Okay. okay.

27
00:01:49.692 --> 00:01:53.113
I knew taking this fare was a mistake.
Now I'm screwed.

28
00:01:58.034 --> 00:01:59.077
[music fades]

29
00:02:00.912 --> 00:02:02.580
[tires screech]

30
00:02:07.001 --> 00:02:09.379
Sorry. guys. I just can't get through.

31
00:02:11.589 --> 00:02:13.842
[taxi drives away]

32
00:02:17.804 --> 00:02:20.557
[Se-ah] Ha-joon. are you sure
this is the right way?

33
00:02:21.307 --> 00:02:22.308
I think so.

34
00:02:24.018 --> 00:02:25.228
Don't worry. Follow me.

35
00:02:27.272 --> 00:02:29.274
[owl hoots]

36
00:02:29.357 --> 00:02:31.359
[suspenseful music plays]

37
00:02:39.409 --> 00:02:40.869
[panting]

38
00:02:46.332 --> 00:02:48.501
[panting]

39
00:03:05.685 --> 00:03:07.729
-[Se-ah] Ha-joon.
-What's wrong?

40
00:03:10.440 --> 00:03:12.442
Are you really sure this is the right way?

41
00:03:13.693 --> 00:03:14.527
Uh-huh.

42
00:03:19.866 --> 00:03:21.451
-[screams]
-[Ha-joon] What's wrong?

43
00:03:21.534 --> 00:03:23.912
-[Se-ah] Bugs!
-[Ha-joon] What is it? Se-ah. wait up!

44
00:03:23.995 --> 00:03:28.583
[Se-ah screams]

45
00:03:28.666 --> 00:03:30.877
Oh! [sighs] Oh.

46
00:03:30.960 --> 00:03:32.795
[Ha-joon] Se-ah. hold up. Wait!

47
00:03:32.879 --> 00:03:34.714
[Se-ah breathes heavily]

48
00:03:36.341 --> 00:03:38.343
Oh shit. Where are we?

49
00:03:38.426 --> 00:03:41.512
[both panting]

50
00:03:50.063 --> 00:03:50.939
Stay close.

51
00:03:53.942 --> 00:03:57.237
[tense music plays]

52
00:04:17.882 --> 00:04:21.928
IF WISHES COULD KILL

53
00:04:22.011 --> 00:04:23.179
[banging on gate]

54
00:04:23.263 --> 00:04:24.138
[music stops]

55
00:04:25.098 --> 00:04:27.392
[Se-ah] Are you sure
someone actually lives here?

56
00:04:27.475 --> 00:04:28.559
[Ha-joon] I think so.

57
00:04:29.894 --> 00:04:31.187
[Se-ah] You think so?

58
00:04:32.230 --> 00:04:33.606
You said you've been here.

59
00:04:34.482 --> 00:04:35.900
I've never been inside.

60
00:04:37.777 --> 00:04:38.611
What?

61
00:04:41.322 --> 00:04:44.909
There's also a guy here. He's super weird.
and he guards this house like a bouncer.

62
00:04:45.910 --> 00:04:48.121
And every time I come here.
he blocks the door and goes.

63
00:04:48.204 --> 00:04:50.123
"You can't come in unless you're invited."

64
00:04:50.206 --> 00:04:53.293
Why would you need to be invited?
You should be able to visit your sister.

65
00:04:53.376 --> 00:04:55.670
I know! But I can't talk to this guy.

66
00:04:55.753 --> 00:04:59.299
I told him I wouldn't go inside. but maybe
my sister could meet me outside. He saidâ€¦

67
00:05:00.300 --> 00:05:02.093
He said. if my sister
were to leave this house.

68
00:05:02.969 --> 00:05:04.012
she would die.

69
00:05:05.179 --> 00:05:07.098
He could've just said
she didn't want to see me.

70
00:05:08.391 --> 00:05:10.226
There's another thing I really hate.

71
00:05:11.227 --> 00:05:13.104
You know what this weirdo calls me?
He calls me--

72
00:05:17.650 --> 00:05:18.484
Brother-in-law.

73
00:05:19.152 --> 00:05:20.528
[intriguing music plays]

74
00:05:20.611 --> 00:05:22.238
I told you not to call me that.

75
00:05:23.656 --> 00:05:25.241
-Hello there.
-Hi.

76
00:05:28.536 --> 00:05:30.997
It's a pleasure to meet you.
Welcome. brother-in-law.

77
00:05:31.080 --> 00:05:32.040
[door creaks]

78
00:05:35.418 --> 00:05:36.544
[music stops]

79
00:05:36.627 --> 00:05:38.254
[Ha-joon] Can we walk a little faster?

80
00:05:38.338 --> 00:05:40.214
Your sister said you'd be coming.
brother-in-law.

81
00:05:40.298 --> 00:05:43.676
-Knock it off.
-Sorry. She's excited to see you. Ha-joon.

82
00:05:43.760 --> 00:05:46.179
-She's been waiting for you all day.
-[Ha-joon] Don't touch me.

83
00:05:46.262 --> 00:05:48.097
-Right up here. Let's go.
-[cell phone buzzes]

84
00:05:48.181 --> 00:05:49.849
GEON-WOO

85
00:05:54.562 --> 00:05:55.521
[Geon-woo] <i>Se-ah?</i>

86
00:05:56.064 --> 00:05:58.107
Mm. Is everything okay?

87
00:05:58.191 --> 00:05:59.984
[Geon-woo] <i>Why haven't you been answering?</i>

88
00:06:01.611 --> 00:06:05.615
<i>I've been trying to get in touch with you.</i>
<i>I was moved to a different room.</i>

89
00:06:06.115 --> 00:06:08.284
<i>-Why haven't you come to see me?</i>
-[Se-ah] Geon-woo.

90
00:06:08.785 --> 00:06:10.036
The thing is

91
00:06:10.620 --> 00:06:12.914
I couldn't make it to see you
because I'm a little far away.

92
00:06:12.997 --> 00:06:15.666
[Geon-woo] <i>No worries. I'll come to you.</i>
<i>Where are you right now?</i>

93
00:06:15.750 --> 00:06:17.085
[eerie music plays]

94
00:06:17.168 --> 00:06:19.253
<i>Se-ah? Hello?</i>

95
00:06:21.756 --> 00:06:23.049
<i>Where should I go?</i>

96
00:06:24.258 --> 00:06:25.760
<i>Tell me where you are.</i>

97
00:06:26.928 --> 00:06:28.012
[door opens]

98
00:06:29.472 --> 00:06:30.848
-Don't answer that!
-[gasps]

99
00:06:30.932 --> 00:06:31.974
[eerie squelching]

100
00:06:41.317 --> 00:06:42.276
[eerie squelching]

101
00:06:42.902 --> 00:06:45.113
[Geon-woo] <i>For fuck's sake!</i>
<i>I asked you where you are!</i>

102
00:06:45.196 --> 00:06:46.864
-Who is that?
-[squeaks]

103
00:06:46.948 --> 00:06:48.658
-[Geon-woo] <i>Answer me now.</i>
-Hang up.

104
00:06:51.953 --> 00:06:53.079
You can't move at all?

105
00:06:57.083 --> 00:06:59.585
-Bangwool. get the rope!
-On it. Brother-in-law. move!

106
00:07:00.128 --> 00:07:00.962
Stay there!

107
00:07:01.045 --> 00:07:04.006
[Geon-woo] <i>If you keep ignoring me.</i>
<i>I'll rip out your boyfriend's tongue.</i>

108
00:07:04.507 --> 00:07:06.050
He doesn't have the power to do that.

109
00:07:06.801 --> 00:07:09.011
[Geon-woo] <i>Remember</i>
<i>how your boyfriend went all ballistic?</i>

110
00:07:09.095 --> 00:07:11.681
<i>Next. I'll throw him against the wall</i>
<i>and smash his fucking skull.</i>

111
00:07:11.764 --> 00:07:14.392
-Wait! What the hell is going on?
-[Bangwool] Brother-in-law. please!

112
00:07:14.475 --> 00:07:16.644
-What are you doing?
-[Bangwool] It's too dangerous!

113
00:07:16.727 --> 00:07:18.813
-What's dangerous?
-Just trust your sister.

114
00:07:21.983 --> 00:07:23.818
[Geon-woo] <i>Do you think</i>
<i>that will save you?</i>

115
00:07:23.901 --> 00:07:27.363
[laughs] <i>You. your boyfriend.</i>
<i>I'll kill you all!</i>

116
00:07:28.573 --> 00:07:32.285
[Geon-woo laughs]

117
00:07:33.119 --> 00:07:35.037
[girl] <i>You wanna play with me. huh?</i>

118
00:07:35.121 --> 00:07:36.414
[Se-ah wheezes]

119
00:07:36.497 --> 00:07:37.582
[girl] <i>Se-ah.</i>

120
00:07:40.251 --> 00:07:41.627
<i>Se-ahâ€¦</i>

121
00:07:43.963 --> 00:07:44.881
<i>Se-ah!</i>

122
00:07:45.381 --> 00:07:48.009
-[girl laughs]
-[Se-ah wheezes]

123
00:07:55.725 --> 00:07:57.310
[Se-ah groans]

124
00:07:57.852 --> 00:07:58.728
[music fades]

125
00:07:58.811 --> 00:08:00.354
-Take her to the altar.
-Don't touch her!

126
00:08:00.438 --> 00:08:03.065
What happened? What did you do to her?

127
00:08:04.525 --> 00:08:07.278
She's been taken by a spirit.
I have to bring her back.

128
00:08:07.361 --> 00:08:08.696
A spirit? What the hell?

129
00:08:08.779 --> 00:08:12.074
There's no time to explain. Ha-joon.
If I don't get her out soon. she'll die.

130
00:08:14.368 --> 00:08:17.955
<i>Do not come out of this room</i>
<i>until Bangwool gives you the signal.</i>

131
00:08:18.039 --> 00:08:20.416
No matter what happens outside.

132
00:08:21.042 --> 00:08:22.001
don't come out.

133
00:08:22.502 --> 00:08:24.128
[tense music plays]

134
00:08:50.821 --> 00:08:54.325
[timer ticks]

135
00:09:05.461 --> 00:09:08.172
Haetsal. Leave what happens outside to me.

136
00:09:08.256 --> 00:09:10.424
Just do what you need to do on the inside.

137
00:09:17.890 --> 00:09:18.891
[sighs]

138
00:09:19.809 --> 00:09:21.727
Good. you're back.

139
00:09:21.811 --> 00:09:23.104
[chuckles]

140
00:09:29.777 --> 00:09:32.321
[Haetsal] Descendant of the Yoo family.
Eighteen years old.

141
00:09:32.989 --> 00:09:34.615
Her name is Se-ah.

142
00:09:34.699 --> 00:09:36.909
[snake hisses]

143
00:09:43.332 --> 00:09:45.960
[snake rattles]

144
00:09:46.043 --> 00:09:48.045
[tense music builds]

145
00:09:51.257 --> 00:09:53.593
Protect the living soul.
and banish the soul of the dead.

146
00:09:53.676 --> 00:09:56.053
May her passage be a safe one.
Please guard this child.

147
00:09:56.804 --> 00:09:59.932
Open the soul door to the light.
Open the spirit door to the light.

148
00:10:00.016 --> 00:10:02.310
Let the soul and spirit enter this vessel.

149
00:10:02.977 --> 00:10:06.063
Cast out all the evil and foul things
beyond the <i>orijeong.</i>

150
00:10:06.647 --> 00:10:10.568
I beseech you
to embrace this child's spirit.

151
00:10:12.445 --> 00:10:13.362
Se-ah.

152
00:10:15.323 --> 00:10:17.116
[echoing] Se-ah. find me.

153
00:10:18.117 --> 00:10:19.910
It's time. child.

154
00:10:22.747 --> 00:10:23.998
-Se-ah!
-[gasps]

155
00:10:24.081 --> 00:10:27.918
[breathes heavily]

156
00:10:39.680 --> 00:10:43.392
[breathes shakily]

157
00:10:49.106 --> 00:10:50.441
-[Haetsal] Se-ah.
-[gasps]

158
00:10:50.524 --> 00:10:51.859
I'm here with you.

159
00:10:53.944 --> 00:10:56.364
I'm here to help you
and direct your strength.

160
00:10:56.447 --> 00:10:57.406
Ha-young?

161
00:10:57.907 --> 00:10:58.741
I don'tâ€¦

162
00:10:58.824 --> 00:11:00.326
Follow my voice.

163
00:11:04.163 --> 00:11:06.290
[breathes shakily]

164
00:11:06.374 --> 00:11:08.459
Where are we? And what do I do?

165
00:11:08.542 --> 00:11:10.419
This is the realm where your curse began.

166
00:11:12.213 --> 00:11:13.172
Don't worry. Se-ah.

167
00:11:13.255 --> 00:11:15.341
I need you to listen to every word I say.

168
00:11:15.424 --> 00:11:18.177
If you can find the first door
and pass through three rooms.

169
00:11:18.260 --> 00:11:19.220
we can get out together.

170
00:11:21.972 --> 00:11:23.391
Where's the door?

171
00:11:24.558 --> 00:11:26.060
How do I know where to go?

172
00:11:26.143 --> 00:11:27.269
[inhales sharply]

173
00:11:27.353 --> 00:11:29.063
Bangwool. We're ready.

174
00:11:29.772 --> 00:11:31.774
[tense percussive music plays]

175
00:11:32.441 --> 00:11:34.443
[wind rushes]

176
00:11:34.527 --> 00:11:36.112
[jingling]

177
00:11:48.666 --> 00:11:50.710
God of doors.

178
00:11:51.585 --> 00:11:55.172
God of doors.
and goddess of fire and hearth.

179
00:11:55.256 --> 00:11:58.801
God of home. God of gates and beams.

180
00:11:58.884 --> 00:12:00.886
Protect us all.

181
00:12:00.970 --> 00:12:03.681
I invoke you to guard this house.

182
00:12:04.390 --> 00:12:08.728
[yells]

183
00:12:59.779 --> 00:13:01.781
[uneasy music plays]

184
00:13:12.208 --> 00:13:13.209
[gasps]

185
00:13:17.004 --> 00:13:19.006
Before you go in.
there's one important rule.

186
00:13:20.883 --> 00:13:23.052
Don't ever look behind you.

187
00:13:23.135 --> 00:13:25.262
Once you pass through a door.
move forward only.

188
00:13:26.013 --> 00:13:29.183
In this realm.
if you see me. they see me as well.

189
00:13:30.643 --> 00:13:31.477
Who?

190
00:13:31.560 --> 00:13:34.146
The spirit that killed your friend
and dragged you here.

191
00:13:36.357 --> 00:13:39.276
If it sees me. all the doors
I made to protect you will be gone.

192
00:13:39.360 --> 00:13:42.404
I don't know.
I don't know if I can do this on my own.

193
00:13:42.988 --> 00:13:44.698
Do you see the thread around your wrist?

194
00:13:48.202 --> 00:13:50.454
This is proof
that you and I are connected.

195
00:13:50.538 --> 00:13:54.416
The door that leads you out of the room
will appear beyond your biggest fears.

196
00:13:55.668 --> 00:13:57.127
The path is not easy.

197
00:13:57.670 --> 00:13:59.505
But have faith that I am right behind you.

198
00:14:01.799 --> 00:14:03.551
[echoing] You can do this. Se-ah.

199
00:14:08.973 --> 00:14:10.140
[Bangwool] Haetsal.

200
00:14:10.224 --> 00:14:12.434
The incense is burning faster than usual.

201
00:14:12.518 --> 00:14:14.937
The doors are going to close quickly.
so be careful.

202
00:14:20.359 --> 00:14:24.488
We've received the message
of the god of life and strength.

203
00:14:24.572 --> 00:14:27.616
Haetsal is seated in the hour of Eul.

204
00:14:27.700 --> 00:14:30.744
May the door not let the evil through.

205
00:14:30.828 --> 00:14:32.079
[Bangwool's voice fades]

206
00:14:35.165 --> 00:14:36.166
[gasps]

207
00:14:37.459 --> 00:14:39.461
[tense eerie music plays]

208
00:15:28.218 --> 00:15:30.679
[unsettling soundscape]

209
00:15:36.060 --> 00:15:40.898
[doors slam]

210
00:15:42.733 --> 00:15:46.278
[breathes shakily]

211
00:16:25.859 --> 00:16:26.694
[click]

212
00:16:26.777 --> 00:16:27.611
[gasps]

213
00:16:28.362 --> 00:16:29.738
-[creaking]
-[light clangs]

214
00:16:32.199 --> 00:16:33.117
[click]

215
00:16:36.328 --> 00:16:37.287
[click]

216
00:16:37.371 --> 00:16:39.540
[Se-ah breathes shakily]

217
00:16:40.124 --> 00:16:40.958
[click]

218
00:16:43.085 --> 00:16:45.337
NURSE'S OFFICE

219
00:16:45.421 --> 00:16:46.296
[clicking]

220
00:16:50.676 --> 00:16:51.510
[click]

221
00:16:52.886 --> 00:16:53.846
[clicking]

222
00:16:55.139 --> 00:16:55.973
[click]

223
00:16:56.724 --> 00:16:59.935
[clicking speeds up]

224
00:17:12.197 --> 00:17:13.115
[clicking stops]

225
00:17:13.657 --> 00:17:16.285
[breathes shakily]

226
00:17:19.913 --> 00:17:23.250
[tapping]

227
00:17:27.463 --> 00:17:29.757
Before you go in.
there's one important rule.

228
00:17:30.382 --> 00:17:32.342
Don't ever look behind you.

229
00:17:32.426 --> 00:17:34.928
Every door is beyond your biggest fears.

230
00:17:37.765 --> 00:17:40.684
Keep looking forward.
Don't look back. no matter what.

231
00:17:40.768 --> 00:17:42.186
[breathes shakily]

232
00:18:06.126 --> 00:18:07.419
-[thud]
-[gasps]

233
00:18:07.503 --> 00:18:09.338
[Se-ah breathes shakily]

234
00:18:09.421 --> 00:18:11.882
[clicking]

235
00:18:14.718 --> 00:18:15.719
Se-ah?

236
00:18:17.221 --> 00:18:19.515
[panicked breathing]

237
00:18:30.609 --> 00:18:32.778
[glass shatters]

238
00:18:36.365 --> 00:18:38.492
[Hyeong-wook] <i>Girigo.</i>
<i>My wish is to get a perfect score.</i>

239
00:18:38.575 --> 00:18:39.868
[Hyeong-wook yells]

240
00:18:40.369 --> 00:18:43.205
[distant screaming]

241
00:18:43.288 --> 00:18:44.790
[tense eerie music builds]

242
00:18:51.380 --> 00:18:52.256
[Hyeong-wook grunts]

243
00:18:55.717 --> 00:18:57.511
[squelching]

244
00:18:57.594 --> 00:18:59.596
[music fades]

245
00:19:01.056 --> 00:19:04.518
[Se-ah breathes shakily]

246
00:19:06.937 --> 00:19:08.147
Hyeong-wook. no.

247
00:19:09.565 --> 00:19:11.567
[dramatic sinister music plays]

248
00:19:13.402 --> 00:19:14.403
[gasps]

249
00:19:18.699 --> 00:19:20.450
[Hyeong-wook] Help me!

250
00:19:23.704 --> 00:19:24.705
Se-ah.

251
00:19:24.788 --> 00:19:25.873
[music stops]

252
00:19:27.332 --> 00:19:31.128
[breathes shakily]

253
00:19:34.047 --> 00:19:35.424
[quiet ominous music plays]

254
00:19:36.300 --> 00:19:37.509
This is your fault.

255
00:19:38.010 --> 00:19:40.012
[breathes shakily]

256
00:19:40.095 --> 00:19:42.264
I don't wanna die alone.

257
00:19:42.973 --> 00:19:44.057
[cries]

258
00:19:44.141 --> 00:19:45.601
Se-ah!

259
00:19:45.684 --> 00:19:47.060
I was wrong.

260
00:19:47.144 --> 00:19:49.938
[Hyeong-wook sobs]

261
00:19:50.022 --> 00:19:52.191
-Please help me.
-It's okay.

262
00:19:52.274 --> 00:19:56.111
[sobs]

263
00:19:56.195 --> 00:19:58.113
[wheezes]

264
00:19:58.197 --> 00:19:59.615
[clicking]

265
00:20:00.157 --> 00:20:03.744
No! Please. Se-ah! It's happening again!

266
00:20:03.827 --> 00:20:05.120
[breathes shakily]

267
00:20:05.204 --> 00:20:06.580
[whimpers]

268
00:20:06.663 --> 00:20:10.667
Agh. stop it! Stop it! Make it stop!

269
00:20:10.751 --> 00:20:13.629
Se-ah!

270
00:20:13.712 --> 00:20:15.881
[Hyeong-wook wails]

271
00:20:21.303 --> 00:20:24.806
[panicked breathing]

272
00:20:31.605 --> 00:20:34.066
[ominous music crescendos]

273
00:20:35.234 --> 00:20:37.569
[breathes shakily]

274
00:20:37.653 --> 00:20:39.655
[tense music plays]

275
00:20:41.073 --> 00:20:42.074
[gasps]

276
00:20:44.076 --> 00:20:47.663
[breathes shakily]

277
00:20:47.746 --> 00:20:48.622
[knife slices]

278
00:20:50.624 --> 00:20:51.750
[chuckles]

279
00:20:52.459 --> 00:20:55.420
[flesh squelches]

280
00:20:57.089 --> 00:21:00.217
[Hyeong-wook laughs maniacally]

281
00:21:02.970 --> 00:21:06.765
[breathes shakily]

282
00:21:09.309 --> 00:21:11.019
What's happening to me? I'm a loser.

283
00:21:11.103 --> 00:21:12.980
[unsettling music plays]

284
00:21:18.735 --> 00:21:19.695
[Hyeong-wook] <i>Se-ah.</i>

285
00:21:19.778 --> 00:21:21.905
[echoing] I had
a really weird phone call earlier.

286
00:21:23.532 --> 00:21:25.450
It was your number on the screen.

287
00:21:25.951 --> 00:21:27.411
And it sounded like you.

288
00:21:27.494 --> 00:21:30.998
A voice just like yours
making fun of me with the others.

289
00:21:33.083 --> 00:21:34.710
Only it wasn't you.

290
00:21:35.252 --> 00:21:37.713
[unsettling music intensifies]

291
00:21:40.799 --> 00:21:43.302
[laughs maniacally]

292
00:21:46.388 --> 00:21:47.764
[laughs]

293
00:21:48.598 --> 00:21:50.350
You're not my friend. You're nothing.

294
00:21:52.853 --> 00:21:54.813
You think
you're so intimidating and scary?

295
00:21:55.397 --> 00:21:56.481
[wheezes]

296
00:21:56.565 --> 00:21:58.775
You're not even real.

297
00:22:00.527 --> 00:22:01.862
[dramatic music plays]

298
00:22:05.073 --> 00:22:06.033
[Se-ah gasps]

299
00:22:06.533 --> 00:22:08.952
[panting]

300
00:22:11.621 --> 00:22:12.581
[flesh squelches]

301
00:22:14.374 --> 00:22:17.419
Leave me alone!

302
00:22:18.337 --> 00:22:19.713
[squelching continues]

303
00:22:19.796 --> 00:22:21.256
[laughs]

304
00:22:21.340 --> 00:22:22.215
[Se-ah screams]

305
00:22:22.299 --> 00:22:24.217
[tense eerie music plays]

306
00:22:25.385 --> 00:22:28.930
[breathes shakily]

307
00:22:46.865 --> 00:22:48.742
[breathes deeply]

308
00:22:53.955 --> 00:22:58.251
[Haetsal breathes heavily]

309
00:22:59.920 --> 00:23:00.921
[Haetsal gasps]

310
00:23:01.004 --> 00:23:03.340
Bangwool. Prepare the second door.

311
00:23:06.927 --> 00:23:08.929
[suspenseful music plays]

312
00:23:16.978 --> 00:23:18.939
[bells jingle]

313
00:23:19.022 --> 00:23:20.357
[wind blows]

314
00:23:23.568 --> 00:23:25.195
The legs of the Ancients
and the ten kings.

315
00:23:25.278 --> 00:23:28.865
the spirit of the first palace. every wing
of every bird. protect this house.

316
00:23:28.949 --> 00:23:30.992
Every wing. cast your shadow
and keep us unseen.

317
00:23:31.076 --> 00:23:33.703
Conceal this child
and allow her safe passage.

318
00:23:33.787 --> 00:23:36.998
We ask the legs of the world to not bend
and the wingsâ€¦

319
00:23:37.082 --> 00:23:38.041
[screeching]

320
00:23:38.125 --> 00:23:41.753
[crashing]

321
00:23:41.837 --> 00:23:43.004
[screeching]

322
00:23:56.768 --> 00:23:59.020
[breathes heavily]

323
00:23:59.104 --> 00:24:01.106
[tense eerie music plays]

324
00:24:19.374 --> 00:24:21.793
[gentle piano music plays]

325
00:24:21.877 --> 00:24:25.338
Daddy. when I win
my first school competition.

326
00:24:25.422 --> 00:24:27.215
what present will you buy me?

327
00:24:41.313 --> 00:24:42.814
Daddy. come on!

328
00:24:43.648 --> 00:24:44.649
[dad] Mm-hmm.

329
00:24:44.733 --> 00:24:46.693
[breathes shakily]

330
00:24:47.235 --> 00:24:48.987
[tense music plays]

331
00:24:55.744 --> 00:24:58.872
Who gave you the idea
you were getting anything?

332
00:25:02.250 --> 00:25:03.168
[cries]

333
00:25:07.172 --> 00:25:08.298
[dad] I love you.

334
00:25:08.381 --> 00:25:11.259
[cries]

335
00:25:12.928 --> 00:25:13.929
Se-ah.

336
00:25:15.263 --> 00:25:16.139
[gasps]

337
00:25:19.726 --> 00:25:22.896
Okay. love bug.
Your dad needs to concentrate on the road.

338
00:25:23.772 --> 00:25:26.691
[whimpers]

339
00:25:26.775 --> 00:25:30.487
[Se-ah sobs]

340
00:25:32.155 --> 00:25:34.157
-Mom!
-[mom] Watch out!

341
00:25:34.241 --> 00:25:35.659
[tires screech]

342
00:25:35.742 --> 00:25:39.412
[car crashes]

343
00:25:44.292 --> 00:25:45.919
[jingling]

344
00:25:48.588 --> 00:25:50.799
[Haetsal] Se-ah. We have to go.

345
00:25:55.554 --> 00:25:57.138
[gentle piano music plays]

346
00:26:03.144 --> 00:26:04.020
[wheezes]

347
00:26:15.365 --> 00:26:17.617
[tense music sting]

348
00:26:19.995 --> 00:26:21.079
[mom] Se-ah?

349
00:26:21.580 --> 00:26:23.039
Is it you?

350
00:26:23.123 --> 00:26:26.251
[Haetsal] There's not much time left.
Please!

351
00:26:26.334 --> 00:26:27.961
We have to find the door.

352
00:26:29.087 --> 00:26:30.005
[sniffles]

353
00:26:31.214 --> 00:26:34.634
[Se-ah cries]

354
00:26:42.100 --> 00:26:45.353
Less than a third left. If you stay in
there. I'm coming in and pulling you out!

355
00:26:45.437 --> 00:26:47.897
[Haetsal] No one should be left alone
in a place like this.

356
00:26:47.981 --> 00:26:49.482
If I have to. I'll take off my mask.

357
00:26:49.566 --> 00:26:52.736
Don't you dare. Absolutely not!
Listen to me. Haetsal!

358
00:26:54.404 --> 00:26:57.198
If you go in there without your mask.
both of you will be trapped.

359
00:26:57.699 --> 00:26:59.034
Stop it now!

360
00:27:00.410 --> 00:27:02.329
I won't let you throw everything away.

361
00:27:03.830 --> 00:27:05.790
I'm begging you. Please.

362
00:27:06.458 --> 00:27:08.126
[cell phone buzzes]

363
00:27:08.209 --> 00:27:10.337
NA-RI

364
00:27:16.593 --> 00:27:18.303
[Se-ah's mom] Oh. my sweet girl.

365
00:27:18.803 --> 00:27:19.679
Mom.

366
00:27:19.763 --> 00:27:21.723
[mom] We didn't have enough time
to truly know you

367
00:27:21.806 --> 00:27:24.934
or watch you grow up
before we left you on your own.

368
00:27:26.353 --> 00:27:28.772
I'm so sorry.

369
00:27:28.855 --> 00:27:31.232
If I could've left this place.

370
00:27:31.316 --> 00:27:33.652
I would have found my way back to you.

371
00:27:35.403 --> 00:27:39.324
I've been waiting for you for so long.
I missed you.

372
00:27:39.908 --> 00:27:41.743
Oh. my sweet girl.

373
00:27:42.410 --> 00:27:44.663
Can you stay with me a little longer

374
00:27:44.746 --> 00:27:48.041
so I can see the beautiful woman
you've grown into?

375
00:27:48.917 --> 00:27:51.169
[Bangwool] Once the door closes.
it's over for both of you.

376
00:27:51.252 --> 00:27:54.506
The plan's not working!
We'll think of something else. Haetsal.

377
00:27:57.008 --> 00:27:58.176
GIRIGO INSTALLED
OPEN

378
00:27:58.259 --> 00:28:00.804
GIRIGO
MAKE A WISH

379
00:28:00.887 --> 00:28:01.971
[music fades]

380
00:28:02.639 --> 00:28:03.932
NOVEMBER 24. 2008
KANG

381
00:28:04.974 --> 00:28:06.059
I'm sorry.

382
00:28:08.728 --> 00:28:09.938
But. Mom.

383
00:28:10.021 --> 00:28:11.272
I can't stay.

384
00:28:12.732 --> 00:28:13.566
[sniffles]

385
00:28:14.317 --> 00:28:15.402
[mom screams]

386
00:28:15.485 --> 00:28:16.695
[mom] Come back!

387
00:28:16.778 --> 00:28:20.865
If you don't turn around.
I'll be in pain and damned here forever!

388
00:28:20.949 --> 00:28:22.742
Se-ah! Please!

389
00:28:22.826 --> 00:28:23.827
Look at me!

390
00:28:23.910 --> 00:28:24.744
[screams]

391
00:28:24.828 --> 00:28:25.912
Se-ah!

392
00:28:26.496 --> 00:28:28.248
Turn around right now!

393
00:28:28.331 --> 00:28:32.168
Otherwise. your dad and I
will burn here for eternity! [screams]

394
00:28:32.252 --> 00:28:33.962
We don't want to die!

395
00:28:34.045 --> 00:28:37.173
Se-ah. look at me! Look at us!

396
00:28:37.257 --> 00:28:39.092
[screams]

397
00:28:39.175 --> 00:28:40.927
[gasps]

398
00:28:41.010 --> 00:28:42.011
[Bangwool] Se-ah.

399
00:28:42.095 --> 00:28:43.221
Se-ah.

400
00:28:43.930 --> 00:28:44.973
Tell us you're okay.

401
00:28:45.473 --> 00:28:48.226
-[breathes heavily]
-[Bangwool] You want to sit up?

402
00:28:52.230 --> 00:28:53.815
Take it easy. Just breathe.

403
00:28:54.607 --> 00:28:56.901
[breathes heavily]

404
00:28:58.194 --> 00:29:00.947
[Bangwool] You did so well.
You should be proud of yourself.

405
00:29:01.030 --> 00:29:03.491
I shouldn't have dragged you
all the way out here.

406
00:29:04.284 --> 00:29:05.660
I'm sorry I put you through this.

407
00:29:06.661 --> 00:29:09.205
-And Ha-young?
-Changing out of her clothes and resting.

408
00:29:09.998 --> 00:29:11.666
This stuff takes a toll on her.

409
00:29:11.750 --> 00:29:13.376
[breathes deeply]

410
00:29:13.460 --> 00:29:14.419
[Bangwool chuckles]

411
00:29:14.502 --> 00:29:16.504
[Haetsal] <i>Se-ah. can you hear me?</i>

412
00:29:16.588 --> 00:29:18.131
[tense music plays]

413
00:29:21.426 --> 00:29:23.219
Are you hearing
someone else talking to you?

414
00:29:24.721 --> 00:29:26.931
[Haetsal] <i>Don't answer him. Just listen.</i>

415
00:29:28.183 --> 00:29:31.352
-Is there somebody else in this room?
-[Haetsal] <i>None of this is real.</i>

416
00:29:31.853 --> 00:29:33.646
<i>This is the third space.</i>

417
00:29:33.730 --> 00:29:35.690
What is it? What's wrong with her?
What's going on?

418
00:29:35.774 --> 00:29:37.817
Something could've latched on her
from the other side.

419
00:29:37.901 --> 00:29:41.029
When the door collapsed. Se-ah. I think
it crossed with you over to this side.

420
00:29:41.529 --> 00:29:44.199
[Haetsal] <i>Notice I'm not there right now?</i>
<i>Ask them to call me.</i>

421
00:29:45.283 --> 00:29:47.911
<i>They won't be able to</i>
<i>because I'm still wearing the mask.</i>

422
00:29:47.994 --> 00:29:50.413
Can you call Ha-young?
I'd like to speak to her.

423
00:29:50.497 --> 00:29:52.123
-Okay. I'll get her right now.
-No. wait.

424
00:29:53.041 --> 00:29:54.876
They're looking for Haetsal
from the other side?

425
00:29:55.502 --> 00:29:57.587
They're using her weakened state
to take advantage.

426
00:29:59.547 --> 00:30:01.508
[breathes deeply]

427
00:30:01.591 --> 00:30:03.009
The spirit has latched on you.

428
00:30:06.179 --> 00:30:07.055
Se-ah.

429
00:30:07.138 --> 00:30:08.556
Listen carefully.

430
00:30:08.640 --> 00:30:11.476
Remember Haetsal told you
to never look behind you. no matter what?

431
00:30:11.559 --> 00:30:13.978
And if you did.
the spirits will be able to see her too?

432
00:30:14.062 --> 00:30:15.563
You have to look behind.

433
00:30:17.774 --> 00:30:19.651
So I can see it too.
Then I can deal with it.

434
00:30:19.734 --> 00:30:20.819
[Haetsal] <i>Don't look back!</i>

435
00:30:20.902 --> 00:30:23.321
<i>He's trying to fool you.</i>
<i>Find the door and get out of there.</i>

436
00:30:30.495 --> 00:30:31.746
Those doors are not the way out.

437
00:30:32.247 --> 00:30:35.458
Remember when you collapsed at our gate
as you were about to enter the house?

438
00:30:35.959 --> 00:30:37.627
[Haetsal] <i>Stay calm. Breathe.</i>

439
00:30:37.710 --> 00:30:39.295
<i>-Find a way out!</i>
-There's nowhere to go!

440
00:30:40.296 --> 00:30:41.673
[Haetsal] <i>Leave. Quickly!</i>

441
00:30:42.382 --> 00:30:43.550
<i>Listen to my voice.</i>

442
00:30:44.050 --> 00:30:46.427
Um. I don't know what's real.

443
00:30:46.928 --> 00:30:48.805
Um. Iâ€¦ I don't know anymore!

444
00:30:49.389 --> 00:30:50.390
[Ha-joon yelps]

445
00:30:50.890 --> 00:30:52.767
-What's wrong?
-[Ha-joon whimpers]

446
00:30:56.187 --> 00:30:57.564
[Ha-joon yelps]

447
00:30:57.647 --> 00:30:59.649
[Ha-joon whimpers]

448
00:31:00.775 --> 00:31:02.694
Se-ah! Se-ah. who is that?

449
00:31:02.777 --> 00:31:04.696
[Ha-joon breathes shakily]

450
00:31:04.779 --> 00:31:06.406
Seâ€¦ Is thatâ€¦

451
00:31:06.990 --> 00:31:09.909
Is that what you guys
have been seeing all along?

452
00:31:09.993 --> 00:31:11.578
Why are you acting like this?

453
00:31:12.745 --> 00:31:14.414
Hâ€¦ how is that possible?

454
00:31:14.497 --> 00:31:18.209
I panicked. [breathes shakily]
It looked like you were dying.

455
00:31:19.168 --> 00:31:20.795
So I also made a wish.

456
00:31:20.879 --> 00:31:21.754
[timer ticks]

457
00:31:21.838 --> 00:31:23.214
[dramatic music plays]

458
00:31:23.298 --> 00:31:25.508
[panicked breathing]

459
00:31:25.592 --> 00:31:26.467
[screams]

460
00:31:26.551 --> 00:31:28.636
Go! Get away! Get out!

461
00:31:28.720 --> 00:31:29.679
[Ha-joon screams]

462
00:31:29.762 --> 00:31:32.223
The only way to save your friend
is to look behind you.

463
00:31:32.307 --> 00:31:34.100
-So turn around!
-[Ha-joon] There!

464
00:31:34.893 --> 00:31:36.019
[Se-ah] Ha-joon. no!

465
00:31:36.561 --> 00:31:38.521
[bones creak]

466
00:31:38.605 --> 00:31:41.608
[Se-ah breathes heavily]

467
00:31:41.691 --> 00:31:44.235
-[Bangwool] Look. Before it's too late!
-Oh God. help me!

468
00:31:44.319 --> 00:31:46.237
-Make it stop!
-[Bangwool] Look. damn it! Look!

469
00:31:46.321 --> 00:31:47.906
Se-ah. help me! Se-ah!

470
00:31:49.949 --> 00:31:50.909
[girl] Found you.

471
00:31:50.992 --> 00:31:52.201
[unsettling music plays]

472
00:31:52.285 --> 00:31:53.286
[Haetsal gasps]

473
00:31:53.953 --> 00:31:55.288
[Haetsal chokes]

474
00:31:55.371 --> 00:31:57.874
Haetsal! Are you out?

475
00:31:58.458 --> 00:32:00.501
-Tell me.
-[Haetsal] It found me.

476
00:32:00.585 --> 00:32:03.171
I have to fight my way out now.
Open the door again.

477
00:32:03.254 --> 00:32:06.132
If I open the door again.
you only get three minutes. That's it.

478
00:32:07.175 --> 00:32:08.259
[Bangwool sighs]

479
00:32:09.218 --> 00:32:11.220
[silence]

480
00:32:16.851 --> 00:32:20.730
[shaky breathing]

481
00:32:21.898 --> 00:32:23.900
[tense eerie music plays]

482
00:32:28.863 --> 00:32:29.864
[ticking]

483
00:32:29.948 --> 00:32:30.949
[water splashes]

484
00:32:31.032 --> 00:32:32.241
[gasps]

485
00:32:33.326 --> 00:32:35.328
[breathes shakily]

486
00:32:45.797 --> 00:32:47.006
[creaking]

487
00:32:47.090 --> 00:32:49.092
[ominous ticking continues]

488
00:32:52.679 --> 00:32:55.348
[creaking]

489
00:32:56.015 --> 00:32:59.560
[Se-ah breathes shakily]

490
00:33:00.353 --> 00:33:02.605
[creaking]

491
00:33:07.402 --> 00:33:10.321
[creaking]

492
00:33:10.405 --> 00:33:12.407
[splashing]

493
00:33:14.909 --> 00:33:17.245
[creaking]

494
00:33:19.956 --> 00:33:21.165
[ticking stops]

495
00:33:26.629 --> 00:33:28.172
[Se-ah gasps]

496
00:33:28.840 --> 00:33:31.509
[creaking]

497
00:33:32.093 --> 00:33:33.678
[breathes shakily]

498
00:33:33.761 --> 00:33:36.806
[creaking]

499
00:33:36.889 --> 00:33:38.558
[unsettling music plays]

500
00:33:47.108 --> 00:33:48.484
[wheezes]

501
00:33:50.737 --> 00:33:54.240
[splutters]

502
00:33:55.116 --> 00:33:57.785
[Se-ah wheezes]

503
00:34:00.413 --> 00:34:02.707
[chokes]

504
00:34:04.709 --> 00:34:07.420
[eerie whooshing]

505
00:34:08.629 --> 00:34:09.714
[breathes shakily]

506
00:34:10.423 --> 00:34:11.424
[Haetsal] Se-ah!

507
00:34:14.260 --> 00:34:15.845
We need to stay connected.

508
00:34:20.600 --> 00:34:23.227
We have to get you through that door. Run!

509
00:34:23.311 --> 00:34:25.188
[tense eerie music plays]

510
00:34:25.271 --> 00:34:27.106
[ticking]

511
00:34:36.699 --> 00:34:38.076
[Haetsal grunts]

512
00:34:38.159 --> 00:34:39.243
[Haetsal yells]

513
00:34:40.870 --> 00:34:43.831
[breathes heavily]

514
00:34:45.041 --> 00:34:46.167
[music fades]

515
00:34:50.630 --> 00:34:51.631
Ha-young?

516
00:34:52.215 --> 00:34:54.133
[gentle music plays]

517
00:34:54.217 --> 00:34:57.053
[Haetsal] It's over now. Just rest.

518
00:35:12.110 --> 00:35:13.111
[chuckles]

519
00:35:14.695 --> 00:35:15.863
Brother-in-law!

520
00:35:16.864 --> 00:35:18.449
[gasps softly]

521
00:35:21.452 --> 00:35:22.286
[gasps]

522
00:35:22.370 --> 00:35:23.329
Se-ah. are you okay?

523
00:35:23.412 --> 00:35:26.499
No. don't worry about me.
I'm totally fine.

524
00:35:26.999 --> 00:35:28.876
She'll go back to being herself. right?

525
00:35:31.045 --> 00:35:33.422
-Is that blood?
-So you do care about me.

526
00:35:34.590 --> 00:35:35.758
She'll be fine for now.

527
00:35:35.842 --> 00:35:38.886
But I'm sorry to say
our fight is not finished yet.

528
00:35:38.970 --> 00:35:39.804
How?

529
00:35:39.887 --> 00:35:43.224
We've severed the thread
to the other side. but only momentarily.

530
00:35:44.225 --> 00:35:45.935
To end this for good.

531
00:35:47.186 --> 00:35:49.105
we have to find the <i>maehyung</i>
and get rid of it.

532
00:35:49.188 --> 00:35:50.231
[Bangwool] Your arm.

533
00:35:50.314 --> 00:35:52.942
Don't make a fuss.
Take care of the kids first.

534
00:35:53.025 --> 00:35:56.279
-Ha-joon. can you move Se-ah inside?
-Yeah.

535
00:36:00.324 --> 00:36:01.450
Show me your arm.

536
00:36:02.660 --> 00:36:04.203
Stop. I told you. it's nothing.

537
00:36:06.080 --> 00:36:07.498
You call that nothing?

538
00:36:07.582 --> 00:36:10.543
If you keep using that power.
you'll never be able to leave this house.

539
00:36:10.626 --> 00:36:12.170
It'll get harder and harder.

540
00:36:12.670 --> 00:36:14.005
[Haetsal] I know.

541
00:36:14.714 --> 00:36:17.508
Look after the kids.
and I'll tend my own wounds. okay?

542
00:36:20.344 --> 00:36:21.387
[exhales]

543
00:36:21.470 --> 00:36:23.097
-[Haetsal] Okay?
-[sighs]

544
00:36:23.181 --> 00:36:24.098
[music stops]

545
00:36:35.651 --> 00:36:37.320
[snake hisses]

546
00:36:42.074 --> 00:36:44.076
[quiet tense music plays]

547
00:36:58.007 --> 00:36:59.175
[music fades]

548
00:37:00.927 --> 00:37:02.678
Oh. Na-ri?

549
00:37:03.471 --> 00:37:04.388
Na-ri!

550
00:37:06.557 --> 00:37:08.100
You still haven't gone home?

551
00:37:08.768 --> 00:37:10.019
Uh. no. not yet.

552
00:37:10.102 --> 00:37:12.063
Ah. You're looking for Geon-woo?

553
00:37:12.647 --> 00:37:14.565
-He's not in the ICU anymore.
-Really?

554
00:37:14.649 --> 00:37:17.401
He's much better.
so we moved him to another ward.

555
00:37:18.402 --> 00:37:19.987
[exhales] Thank God.

556
00:37:20.071 --> 00:37:21.405
That's great news.

557
00:37:22.031 --> 00:37:23.324
How is he doing now?

558
00:37:24.033 --> 00:37:26.953
He regained consciousness
about an hour ago.

559
00:37:27.036 --> 00:37:30.539
-You can see him. He's allowed visitors.
-[sighs] Great. I'll do that.

560
00:37:30.623 --> 00:37:31.540
[chuckles]

561
00:37:34.085 --> 00:37:37.213
-[Ha-joon chokes]
-[Geon-woo laughs maniacally]

562
00:37:37.296 --> 00:37:39.298
[uneasy music plays]

563
00:37:40.841 --> 00:37:42.093
I really did that?

564
00:37:45.638 --> 00:37:47.431
I don't want to give you bad news.

565
00:37:47.515 --> 00:37:50.810
but Se-ah said. after that.
she couldn't bear to see you.

566
00:37:51.435 --> 00:37:53.145
That's why I'm the only one here.

567
00:37:57.358 --> 00:37:58.442
[music fades]

568
00:38:01.737 --> 00:38:03.656
Get to the point.
Why'd you call me out here?

569
00:38:05.324 --> 00:38:06.284
[Bangwool groans]

570
00:38:07.159 --> 00:38:07.994
Scooch.

571
00:38:19.588 --> 00:38:21.716
Planning on making a wish? Hm?

572
00:38:21.799 --> 00:38:23.592
[groans] Ow!

573
00:38:24.135 --> 00:38:26.387
[groans] Why the hell did you hit me?

574
00:38:26.971 --> 00:38:28.639
-[groans]
-Don't ever do that again.

575
00:38:28.723 --> 00:38:30.975
It only makes things harder
for your sister.

576
00:38:32.685 --> 00:38:36.022
If you cause her more harm. I'll forbid
you to visit at all. brother-in-law.

577
00:38:39.233 --> 00:38:42.111
[groans] Besides. didn't you come
all this way to earn her trust?

578
00:38:42.194 --> 00:38:43.154
Or not?

579
00:38:43.237 --> 00:38:45.614
Then why don't you start
trusting her already?

580
00:38:46.991 --> 00:38:49.910
I'm begging. okay? Please.
Oh. please. and blah. blah.

581
00:38:51.871 --> 00:38:52.955
Brother-in-law.

582
00:39:03.924 --> 00:39:05.801
I wish he would stop calling me that.

583
00:39:10.348 --> 00:39:13.559
Here are some clean clothes.
We need to burn the ones you were wearing.

584
00:39:16.187 --> 00:39:17.229
Your arm.

585
00:39:17.313 --> 00:39:18.856
I thought you hurt it.

586
00:39:19.815 --> 00:39:21.734
-[Haetsal] Oh.
-[Se-ah] I'm sorry.

587
00:39:22.485 --> 00:39:25.112
Because I didn't trust you.
now you're in danger.

588
00:39:25.196 --> 00:39:29.075
It's me who should apologize. You came
this far and I couldn't see it through.

589
00:39:29.158 --> 00:39:30.993
I never asked you about your past.

590
00:39:31.077 --> 00:39:33.496
I just told you to keep on going.
no matter what.

591
00:39:34.246 --> 00:39:36.707
I shouldn't have let you see
such horrible things.

592
00:39:38.751 --> 00:39:40.878
It wasn't all horrible. you know?

593
00:39:42.838 --> 00:39:45.257
It might sound silly or kind of strange.

594
00:39:47.009 --> 00:39:48.052
but it was

595
00:39:49.595 --> 00:39:52.473
nice to see my parents again.
even in that awful place.

596
00:39:53.933 --> 00:39:57.269
-Se-ah.
-I know that it was just an illusion.

597
00:39:57.353 --> 00:39:59.355
[tense music plays]

598
00:39:59.438 --> 00:40:01.649
-But still--
-Not everything was fake in there.

599
00:40:02.358 --> 00:40:04.235
Your real memories were mixed in.

600
00:40:04.318 --> 00:40:07.696
Memories so painful
you had to bury them in your subconscious.

601
00:40:08.864 --> 00:40:11.325
I'm sure your mom
who tried to save you was real.

602
00:40:11.409 --> 00:40:14.537
Whatever that spirit is. it was trying
to use your memories against you.

603
00:40:15.121 --> 00:40:16.330
And that's not fair.

604
00:40:19.208 --> 00:40:21.293
-Ha-Young?
-Hm?

605
00:40:21.377 --> 00:40:24.255
Please help me finish this
so it doesn't happen again.

606
00:40:24.338 --> 00:40:26.132
[gentle music plays]

607
00:40:26.215 --> 00:40:29.969
You're the only one
who can stop that girl on the other side

608
00:40:30.845 --> 00:40:32.471
once and for all.

609
00:40:34.348 --> 00:40:35.307
[electronic music sting]

610
00:40:35.391 --> 00:40:37.435
[Haetsal] This app
that you guys call Girigo

611
00:40:38.227 --> 00:40:41.689
is a strong curse
created by a vengeful spirit.

612
00:40:41.772 --> 00:40:45.526
To put an end to this. we need to find
and destroy something called <i>maehyung</i>

613
00:40:45.609 --> 00:40:47.111
that connects our side. where we are.

614
00:40:47.194 --> 00:40:49.363
to the other side.
where the vengeful spirit is.

615
00:40:49.447 --> 00:40:50.448
<i>Maehyung?</i>

616
00:40:50.531 --> 00:40:52.241
Mm-hm. <i>Maehyung.</i>

617
00:40:52.825 --> 00:40:54.326
"Mae" as in "to bury."

618
00:40:55.119 --> 00:40:56.328
And "hyung" as in "cruel."

619
00:40:56.412 --> 00:41:00.249
<i>Maehyung </i>is an object that contains
the essence of a powerful curse.

620
00:41:01.584 --> 00:41:04.420
Do you remember that red phone
that was connected to your wrist

621
00:41:04.503 --> 00:41:05.504
when you saw that girl?

622
00:41:06.922 --> 00:41:08.424
[uneasy music plays]

623
00:41:10.759 --> 00:41:12.887
[eerie squelching]

624
00:41:14.513 --> 00:41:15.347
Yeah.

625
00:41:15.431 --> 00:41:17.808
You need to bring that
to this house right away.

626
00:41:17.892 --> 00:41:19.643
Is it only Se-ah who can do it?

627
00:41:21.312 --> 00:41:24.148
We don't have a choice. Se-ah is
the only person who can hold the phone.

628
00:41:24.732 --> 00:41:27.610
She's also the only one
who's connected to the vengeful spirit.

629
00:41:27.693 --> 00:41:29.320
to me. and the other side.

630
00:41:31.655 --> 00:41:32.656
[music fades]

631
00:41:47.254 --> 00:41:49.924
[Bangwool moans] Oh. brother-in-law.

632
00:41:55.513 --> 00:41:56.847
[thunder rumbles]

633
00:41:58.432 --> 00:42:01.227
[tense music plays]

634
00:42:01.310 --> 00:42:05.648
[squelching]

635
00:42:08.692 --> 00:42:09.527
[Se-ah mumbles]

636
00:42:11.946 --> 00:42:12.780
[mumbles]

637
00:42:25.251 --> 00:42:28.712
-[sinister music plays]
-[ominous squelching]

638
00:42:33.676 --> 00:42:36.220
[breathes heavily]

639
00:42:38.806 --> 00:42:40.808
[eerie ominous music plays]

640
00:44:59.113 --> 00:45:00.280
[music fades]

641
00:45:04.451 --> 00:45:06.453
[eerie rhythmic wind rushing]

642
00:45:37.526 --> 00:45:39.528
[ominous percussive music plays]

643
00:46:20.652 --> 00:46:21.653
[music fades]
